---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer
  class="bg-primary-container dark:bg-tertiary-container w-full border-t border-secondary/20"
>
  <div
    class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-gutter max-w-container-max mx-auto px-gutter py-section-padding-desktop reveal"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-start space-y-4">
      <span class="text-headline-md font-headline-md text-secondary-fixed"
        >Sidre Beauty Center</span
      >
      <p class="text-body-md font-body-md text-on-primary-container/70 max-w-xs">
        Zarif bir sığınakta özel, holistik bakımlar aracılığıyla güzelliği ve
        esenliği yüceltiyoruz.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div></div>
    <div
      class="flex flex-col justify-center items-start md:items-end space-y-2 text-body-md font-body-md text-on-primary-container/70"
    >
      <span>© {year} Sidre Beauty Center. Tüm hakları saklıdır.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
